contentrichtext.text: '''Fateh''' may refer to: ;Language * [[Punjabi language|Punjabi]] and [[Urdu]] for 'Victory' ;Places, Political groups and Masjids * [[Fatah]], a Palestinian political affiliation * [[Fateh Oil Field]], a prominent oil-producing area in the [[Persian Gulf]] near [[Dubai]]. * [[Fateh-110]], a missile * [[Al Fateh Mosque]] * [[El Fateh]], Egyptian city * [[Al Fateh (Sports Club)]], a Saudi sports club * [[Al Fateh]], Hamas children's magazine ;People * [[Fateh (name)]] * [[Fatih (name)]] ;Religion * Fateh, used in the Sikh Greeting "[[Waheguru]] Ji Ka [[Khalsa]], Waheguru Ji Ki Fateh", referring to victory. {{disambiguation}}
